CatDescriptText: Charles Harris is wearing a hat possibly inscribed "Dip."  They are in the living room of Charles "Teenie" Harris' home at 7604 Mulford Street.
TitMainTitle: Scott and Charles A. Harris Jr., sons of Charles A. "Little Teenie" Harris, wearing cowboy costumes, with Scott wearing hat inscribed "Darryl" riding toy steam shovel, in front of Christmas tree with gifts including plaid shirts, Monkeyshines board game, Mighty Mouse target game, and Picture Paints, in Charles "Teenie" Harris' home at 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
